  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And, and [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I remember one time-- we used to go to, to-- in the-- in the summer, we used to go to our grandmother in southern Germany, where my mother was born.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she had a-- she lived in a house that was built in 1736.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's where she had a store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the house belonged to her, a nice house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I still remember that very affectionately, that we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all together they-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I loved the area and the town and the whole areas of Swabia, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] where my mother came from, because it was very different.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Or I thought it was different, maybe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Maybe it was a more childish feeling that people there were different, friendlier, than up in northern Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the-- the country was flat where I grew up, and there were mountains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and the, the towns were, were more cultured.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, the whole atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember one time when we went there when my grandmother was still alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Usually-- but last-- one time after she had died already, my grandmother had died already, we went there and, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and I was looking forward, dreaming of my, my, my-- dreaming of it, you know, looking forward to-- to visiting-- to visit there.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we had to change trains from a-- from an express train to a small, small train.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we got into the small train, there came a group of drunken [? peasants ?] and made a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that already kind of disillusioned me to the south.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and then we-- instead of going to our grandmother's house, we stayed in a hotel.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
